title: Unable to select a cell via the showNotebookDocument cmd
Properly dispose of everything in cells in Ports view
Adding "Delete Branch..." to the Source Control > Branch section
body:
<!-- Thank you for submitting a Pull Request. Please:

* Associate an issue with the Pull Request.

This PR fixes #118138. The `Delete Branch` option has been added to the `Source Control > Branch` section.
